name: Judgment of supreme court final
text:
The judgment of the supreme court in all matters brought before it on appeal, under this chapter, shall be final. [L 1894-5, c 26, §9; RL 1925, §2677; am L 1929, c 213, §3; RL 1935, §4428; RL 1945, §10483; RL 1955, §245-9; HRS ; am L 1972, c 164, §1(g)]
Note
  Section repealed effective July 1, 2006.  L 2004, c 202, §81.
Case Notes
  Cited:  36 H. 603, 605.
